    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and is ideal for someone looking for a dependable daily driver that doesn't need to be showroom perfect. The exterior shows its age with several noticeable scratches, minor door dings, and some fading on the roof's clear coat. Inside, the upholstery is intact but shows moderate wear from regular use. Mechanically, the car starts reliably and runs well, though it will eventually need routine maintenance like new brake pads and a suspension check-up to stay in top shape.",
