    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly a little sad to see this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for a new home. This car is in absolutely incredible shape\u2014honestly, it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve been super meticulous about keeping it spotless inside and out, so it\u2019s basically like new. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s practically perfect and ready for its next adventure, you\u2019ve found it. Come take a look, you won\u2019t be disappointed!",
      "price": 46500.0,
