    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "Presenting a concours-level 2004 Porsche 911 Carrera 4S, featuring the naturally aspirated 3.6L flat-six mated to a crisp 6-speed manual transaxle. This widebody 996.2 showcases impeccable mechanical integrity, featuring a documented IMS bearing retrofit and a flawless rear-main seal. The Viscous Multi-Plate AWD system ensures surgical turn-in, complemented by the factory M030 sport suspension for optimized roll stiffness and precise damping. Every bushing remains pliable, and the throttle response is razor-sharp. With consistent paint depth across all panels and an undercarriage free of oxidation or fluid seepage, this is a true purist's specimen.",
